Package org.anchoranalysis.image.bean.spatial

Class SizeXY

Object
AnchorBean<SizeXY>
SizeXY
public class SizeXY extends AnchorBean<SizeXY>
The size of an entity in the X and Y dimensions.

i.e. the width and height of an entity.

Author:
Owen Feehan
